To run tlm_forecast_tl application with pre-partitioned meshes
===================================================================
* build <LFRic_Core>/mesh_tools
  - Check-out Lfric Core Repository
  - cd <LFRic_Core>/mesh_tools
  - make build

* build <LFRic_Apps>/jedi_lfric_tests
  - Check-out Lfric Apps Repository
  - cd <LFRic_Apps>
  - ./build/local_build.py -a jedi_lfric_tests

* cd <LFRic_Apps>/applications/jedi_lfric_tests/example_tlm_forecast_tl

* Generate the pre-partitioned files
  <LFRic_Core>/mesh_tools/bin/cubedsphere_mesh_generator C12_op.nml

* Run the application
  mpiexec -n 6 ../bin/jedi_tlm_forecast_tl configuration_op.nml
